'''Devil's Chest''' ni filime y'intambara yo muri [[Uganda]] yasohotse 2017 ivuga ku nyeshyamba za Lord Resistance Army mu majyaruguru ya [[Uganda]]<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201709040638.html</ref>. Yanditswe, yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Hassan Mageye hamwe nabakinnyi Hasifah Nande Nakitende na Samuel Rogers Masaaba mu nshingano zabo.<ref>https://amakula.org/film/devils-chest/</ref> Yerekanwe bwa mbere i Gulu mu Kwakira 2017 n i Kampala muri Gicurasi 2019.<ref>https://ugandaradionetwork.net/a/file.php?fileId=114919</ref>  

== Incamake ==
Mu gihe cya Lords Resistance Army (LRA) mu majyaruguru ya [[Uganda]], umugore wo mu mudugudu ahatirwa kuba umugore w’umuyobozi w’inyeshyamba Joseph Kony, umugabo wishe umugabo we. Aba umusirikare kandi arwanira umudendezo<ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/magazine/kony-story-wins-film-of-the-year-1373244</ref>. 

== Kwakira ==
Filime yakiriwe neza muri [[Uganda]] no muri [[Afurika|Afrika]] yose kubera amateka yayo, gukina ndetse nicyerekezo.<ref>https://www.vanguardngr.com/2018/09/amvca-2018-18-hours-emerges-overall-best-movie/</ref>  Yakiriye  ibihembo byinshi (icyenda) mu bihembo bya 5 bya Uganda Film Festival Awards muri 2017 kandi yatsindiye ibihembo bine birimo Filime nziza n’umuyobozi mwiza<ref>https://www.bloombergquint.com/business/warlord-s-fighters-become-movie-stars-as-ugandan-cinema-booms</ref>.   Yatowe kandi mu bihembo bya Afurika Magic Viewers Choice Awards 2018 (AMVCA) ibihembo bya Filime Nziza yo muri [[Afurika]] y'Iburasirazuba na Filime Nziza Muri rusange <ref>https://www.premiumtimesng.com/entertainment/nollywood/274528-2018-amvca-falz-rita-dominic-adesua-etomi-others-emerge-nominees.html</ref>.  Bimwe mubice bya tekiniki, inkuru nibikorwa bya firime ariko byanenzwe<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/lifestyle/who-will-win-big-africas-oscars</ref>. Collins Kakwezi wo mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Amakula yise iyi filime umushinga uteganijwe avuga ko ibikorwa byabuze kandi ko umuyobozi w'inyeshyamba, Joseph Kony yagaragajwe nk'umuntu mwiza binyuze ku mukinnyi Samuel Rogers Masaaba<ref>https://dailynews.co.tz/news/2018-09-045b8e29f9ee02b.aspx</ref>. 

